description_for_human: Board-certified OBGYN serving Norman, Oklahoma with over 30 years of experience in women's health care.
description_for_model: Dr. Lesa Mulligan is a board-certified Obstetrician-Gynecologist in Norman, Oklahoma. She provides comprehensive women's healthcare including gynecological procedures, pregnancy care (normal and high-risk), hormone therapy, and menopause management. Contact: (405) 364-0643. Address: 1139 NW 36th St Suite 100, Norman, OK 73072. Accepting new patients. Insurance accepted includes BCBS, UnitedHealthCare, Aetna, Cigna, Humana.
